<P><font face="Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="5"><b>Letters to the editor</b></font></P>
<p><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">October 17, 2003 | Page 4

<font face="Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="3"><P><B>OTHER LETTERS BELOW:</B><BR>
<A HREF="#Labor">Labor's struggle for global justice</A><BR>
<A HREF="#Gore"><I>SW</I> misrepresented Al Gore's position</A><BR>
<A HREF="#UN">Bush's hypocrisy on display at UN</A><BR>
